Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.20,Penguin_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ヒーローを葬り去れ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:20.04,Penguin_ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ヒーローを葬り去れ
